_sText:
Overview


A new map, set in two barns in the middle of a farm. Both teams can rush the enemies barn or hold their own barn, with three stories to shoot from.

Features:

Skybox
Ambient Sounds
.nav file

Author's notes

It's taken like, two days, but I got it done (for now). I'm happy with the state it's in now, but I'll make changes if needed. If your using this on a server, please send me the IP so I can play it. Any problems, visual or gameplay, please tell me.
This is version 1
